<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q64_v10" title="Probabilidad de complemento en urna" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceA</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float"><qti-default-value><qti-value>0</qti-value></qti-default-value></qti-outcome-declaration><qti-item-body>
    <p>Considera una urna con 36 bolitas entre amarillas, azules y rojas, todas del mismo tipo.</p>
    <p>Al sacar una bolita al azar de la urna, la probabilidad de que esta sea amarilla o azul es 
      <m:math>
        <m:mfrac>
          <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          <m:mn>3</m:mn>
        </m:mfrac>
      </m:math>.
      
      
      
      ¿Cuál es la probabilidad de que la bolita extraída sea roja?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="true" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! La probabilidad de roja es el complemento de “amarilla o azul”, por lo tanto <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math>. Además, con 36 bolitas, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>, así que 12 de 36 pueden ser rojas, lo que confirma <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> es la probabilidad de que la bolita sea amarilla o azul, según el enunciado. La probabilidad de roja debe ser el complemento: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>1</m:mn>
            <m:mn>2</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si la probabilidad de roja fuera <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, entonces la probabilidad de “amarilla o azul” tendría que ser <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math>, pero el enunciado indica <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. Además, con 36 bolitas, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>18</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> rojas dejaría 18 no rojas, y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>18</m:mn><m:mn>36</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">
        <m:math>
          <m:mfrac>
            <m:mn>3</m:mn>
            <m:mn>4</m:mn>
          </m:mfrac>
        </m:math>
        <qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si la probabilidad de roja fuera <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, entonces la probabilidad de “amarilla o azul” sería <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math>, pero el enunciado indica <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. Además, con 36 bolitas, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>27</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> rojas dejaría 9 no rojas, y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>9</m:mn><m:mn>36</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math>, no <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline>
      </qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso por complemento</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Identificar el dato entregado</strong></p>
            <p>El enunciado dice que la probabilidad de sacar una bolita amarilla o azul es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Reconocer el evento complementario</strong></p>
            <p>Las bolitas de la urna son amarillas, azules y rojas. Entonces, “ser roja” es el complemento de “ser amarilla o azul”.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Aplicar la regla del complemento</strong></p>
            <p>La suma de las probabilidades de un evento y su complemento es 1. Por eso:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>P</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>roja</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mi>P</m:mi><m:mrow><m:mo>(</m:mo><m:mtext>amarilla o azul</m:mtext><m:mo>)</m:mo></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 4: Verificación con las 36 bolitas</strong></p>
            <p>Si <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> de 36 bolitas son amarillas o azules, entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, las rojas son:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>36</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>12</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>La probabilidad de roja es:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>12</m:mn><m:mn>36</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La probabilidad de que la bolita extraída sea roja es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>3</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. La alternativa correcta es la A.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>